org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.ws.component

Class NoopMessageFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openhubframework.openhub.core.common.ws.component.NoopMessageFilter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.camel.component.spring.ws.filter.MessageFilter

    @Component
public class NoopMessageFilter
extends Object
implements org.apache.camel.component.spring.ws.filter.MessageFilter
    Does no message filtering (post-processing). Picked up by SpringWebserviceComponent to skip setting camel headers/attachments to outbound SOAP message.

    Used instead of the default BasicMessageFilter, which adds Camel Message headers to Soap Message headers, and Camel Message attachments to Soap Message attachments.
